Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.45,0:00:05.18,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}As times{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10} chan{\r\be10}ge,\Ndifficult cases increase in number!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:06.85,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today's a lodge mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:09.45,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Who's the mysterious bandaged man?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.45,0:00:11.26,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:13.46,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.46,0:00:15.67,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.67,0:01:41.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:45.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The lodge should be right around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:48.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, we're not lost, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:52.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.15,0:01:54.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just taking a little side trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:55.82,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We're lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:03.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:05.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:07.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Someone's walking...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:09.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's going to the lodge too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:21.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's going to the lodge too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:23.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:26.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Ran! What were you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:28.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:31.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nice enough to let you stay at my family's lodge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:33.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and you show up late...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.56,0:02:35.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you'd bring him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:39.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be more considerate, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.50,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}As if you're one to talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:45.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep hanging around this twerp and you'll never fall in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:46.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Love?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:51.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We're here to meet some wonderful guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:53.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And with nature all around us,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:58.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll have dream-like romances with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:03:01.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh yeah, I forgot she's that kind of person...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.92,0:03:06.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? These "wonderful guys" aren't here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:08.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:11.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister's friends got here long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:13.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and are relaxing in their rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.80,0:03:19.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, is one of their faces wrapped in bandages?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:21.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bandages? No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:23.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,None of the people here are hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:25.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we just saw—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:28.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he lives nearby, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:31.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, stop being a weirdo and put your stuff away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.55,0:03:33.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys' room is upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:35.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:42.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, look at all these rooms up here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:46.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:50.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! My mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:02.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go! This is ours, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:05.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, learn to knock before opening doors!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:16.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all from the same circle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:20.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! They all made films together during my sister's college days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:23.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The five closest people got together for the first time in two years!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:25.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next to Ran is Ota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:29.51,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaru Ota (24)\NPresently, Import Car Broker
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:28.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who usually played the leading role!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:29.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:33.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next to him is Sumiya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, our cameraman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:33.98,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroki Sumiya (25)\NPresently, Film Magazine Editor
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:33.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:36.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our stage manager, Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:37.65,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryoichi Takahashi (25)\NPresently, Food Company Employee
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:37.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:40.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:41.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:43.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:46.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:50.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up is our makeup and wardrobe person,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:55.17,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayako Suzuki (24)\NPresently, Graduate Student
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:54.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,my sister, who is also looking for a husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:59.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And last is our director, scriptwriter, and club president—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:05:02.13,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako Ikeda (24)\NPresently, Scriptwriter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:01.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako Ikeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:07.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The same Chikako Ikeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} who wrote the very latest movie, "Blue Kingdom"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:08.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:13.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She wrote it during college and it started her career, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drag up old stories like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:20.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear there's talk about your next movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:23.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}! How about a word for your fans?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:26.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being silly, Sumiya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:29.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You still love to tape things, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:32.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I can't kick the habit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:36.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takahashi! Have you gotten fatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:39.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess I'm about 100 kilograms now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:41.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get you in frame anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:43.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:49.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This certainly brings back memories of college!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:51.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And Atsuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:54.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'd be here now if she hadn't done that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:02.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not talk about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:03.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:10.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I took time out of my busy schedule to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:13.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not talk about someone who died two years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:17.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Celebrities sure do say strange things...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:18.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:20.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:24.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go make dinner now,\Nso just make yourselves at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:27.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll go finish fixing the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:29.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They said it was going to rain this evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:32.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd appreciate that, Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:34.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:39.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like the perfect kind of work for a set designer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:41.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say the rest of us play cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.84,0:06:44.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'll play!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.51,0:06:46.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where're you going, Chikako?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:48.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:57.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi said it's gonna rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Chikako!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:13.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really coming down...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:16.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no enjoying the view now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:18.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:20.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he dreamy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:25.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's like so cool and suave—totally my type!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:27.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:31.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right, you have Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:33.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad he couldn't come with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:37.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As if! I'd bust him upside the head if he were here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:39.40,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He {\i1}is{\i0} here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:43.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say. Would you like to take a walk with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:45.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:49.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're not doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:53.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's raining outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.42,0:07:55.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Walks in the rain can be invigorating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:57.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.93,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:03.56,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}She'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:15.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That lousy Ran! She has Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:17.14,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:19.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll steal Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:20.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No. No, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? There's someone you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:24.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:27.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't know when he'll be back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:30.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should dump the cold-hearted jerk
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:33.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and find a better man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:36.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about I teach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:39.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...what adult love is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:42.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:46.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:47.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:56.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that was a really close one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:08:58.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh no! They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.42,0:09:02.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:03.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:08.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might be lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:14.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:17.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something if you're there! Ota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:27.74,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:38.62,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:41.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you screaming about—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:44.66,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:47.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:49.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A man in bandages?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:52.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He attacked Ran in the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:53.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:56.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You guys didn't see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:59.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't the three of you in the forest too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:02.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just went looking for Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:04.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see anything like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:07.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't see him either, right, Chikako?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:09.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"We"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:10.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You went and disappeared somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:14.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to get an umbrella!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:16.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you weren't afraid of the lightning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:17.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:18.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.79,0:10:20.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:25.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's almost over between them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:28.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you see the guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:30.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran toward the lodge...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:32.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't see anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:34.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see him, Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:37.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was on the roof the entire time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:39.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't remember seeing anyone like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.58,0:10:44.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I did see someone strange by the bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:47.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when I first got here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:49.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't really see his face,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:54.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but he was wearing a black cape and a hood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:57.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That's the person who attacked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:10:58.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:10:59.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:02.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the same guy when I got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:06.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here! But I figured he lived nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:07.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:12.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only 2 or 3 lodges\Non the other side of the bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:14.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and there's a mountain on this side...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:16.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who was that guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:18.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We should call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:19.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:26.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The phone's not working?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:29.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was working this afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:32.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the phones are down because of that lightning strike?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:37.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was him! That bandaged man cut the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:41.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:42.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:43.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:49.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The bridge is out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:04.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The bridge is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:09.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably fell on its own. It was pretty old.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:11.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:13.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone cut it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:18.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this bridge support.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:21.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! It's been chopped up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:24.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody used some sort of blade...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:27.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But who on earth would do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:30.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was that guy! He did this too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:31.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:34.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This "bandaged man" is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:37.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He attacked the girl in the forest,\Ncut the phone line,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:41.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and chopped the bridge down because he enjoys watching us get scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep getting afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:45.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be giving him what he wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:50.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:53.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's dark out, so our only choice
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:56.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is to wait until tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:13:00.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus this "bandaged man" everyone's worked up about
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:02.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,might still be hiding in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:03.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:04.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:13.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:17.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to bed now. I'm suddenly tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:19.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't need any dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:20.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:32.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you help, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:35.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem! I always do this at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:38.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a reunion this has turned into...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:41.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's suddenly unsociable...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:44.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because you mentioned that incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:48.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean about Atsuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:51.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl that had something happen two years ago—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:53.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.01,0:13:57.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She killed herself. Two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:14:00.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a member of our filmmaking group, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:03.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she suddenly hanged herself in her room,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:06.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone stopped meeting after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:09.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We were all so close, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:14.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I asked everyone here\Nfor a long-overdue reunion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:18.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's not talk about that anymore, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:22.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:23.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where's Chikako?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:25.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was tired, so she went to bed early.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:28.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Dinner's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:30.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be down in a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:32.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Is the roof fixed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:33.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, for the most part.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:40.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down here, Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:41.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The food's gonna get cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:42.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:45.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone by the downstairs window!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:51.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.07,0:14:59.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:02.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It's too dark to see where they went!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:05.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:09.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's follow the kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:11.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lock the doors and wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:12.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:13.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Me, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:15.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:27.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:29.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's Chikako's?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:34.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an arm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:36.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's goin' on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:38.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up and look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:41.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako! Chikako!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:43.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:51.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako! Say something! Chikako!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:05.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:08.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she had been murdered...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:10.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...by the time we got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:12.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:14.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, we covered the body with my jacket
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:16.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and left it in the forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:18.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would someone kill Chikako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:20.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:23.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I hadn't planned this reunion,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:26.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she'd still be—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:29.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, Ayako! It's not your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:31.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That bandaged man is to blame!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:34.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That crazed murderer who ran off with Chikako
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,before our very eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:43.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do if he comes back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:46.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine if we lock the place down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:50.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako was careless enough to stroll around outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:54.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's forget about this\Nand get some shut-eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:56.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ota! How can you—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:59.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. It's getting late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:02.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make sure everything is locked and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:06.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll climb down the mountain and get the police tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:06.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:14.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Front door's locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:16.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is our rooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:18.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:21.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s slippers aren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:23.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Slippers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:27.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she went out the front door, her slippers should be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:30.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She might not have left from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:32.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:36.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What if the guy snuck into the lodge
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.33,0:17:38.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and attacked Chikako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} upstairs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:40.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he didn't, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:43.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember? When Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and the others ran after him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:48.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you, Ayako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and I split up and checked all the locks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:51.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room wasn't in shambles,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:55.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the window was locked from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:57.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:18:00.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost certain she went outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:03.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she was wearing shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:06.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her leg had been chopped off, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:08.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:11.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, does this lodge have any other exits?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:13.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:14.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A back door?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:17.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:23.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go! These are definitely Chikako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s slippers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:26.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't leave any spare ones out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:29.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means Chikako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} went out this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:32.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:36.99,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But why did she go out this way\Nand not the front door?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:40.16,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's almost like she was trying to sneak out unseen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:42.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, it's really muddy here—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:44.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,has someone been using this door?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:46.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it was probably my sister—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:48.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the gas switch and stuff is in the backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:51.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we found her slippers,\Nso let's go to bed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:53.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:07.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There! Now our room's okay too, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:08.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:11.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop worrying, everything'll be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:13.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the bandaged man shows up again,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:16.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat him up with my karate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:17.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:22.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yeah, right! When he attacked you in the forest\Nyou were too scared to do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:26.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, why do you think he attacked you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:30.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. Maybe it didn't matter who.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:34.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anybody have a grudge against you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:37.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like anyone whose face you injured with karate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:39.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:41.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:42.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:51.17,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But there's something odd about that bandaged man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:54.97,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If he took Chikako{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}, who left out the back door,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:59.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}then why would he go around to the front door for us to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:02.74,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}To make us afraid? Or perhaps—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:05.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:06.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I sleep with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:08.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.65,0:20:10.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:12.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because you're afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:14.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just because.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:16.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet dreams, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:19.46,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Girls have some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:21.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Now where was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:24.26,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That bandaged man had just—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:30.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}As I was saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:32.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh no! I can't think!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:35.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Well, this {\i1}is{\i0} a crazed murderer we're dealing with;
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:38.28,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}this is a job for the police, not me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:40.01,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Time for sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:41.53,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Can I sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:41.11,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He's after Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.85,0:22:43.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:45.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.76,0:22:46.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:52.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:55.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh no! I sprained my ankle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:57.40,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Once Ran falls asleep, there's no waking her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.40,0:22:59.74,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Isn't there anything around here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.74,0:23:02.27,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's it! The Voice-Altering Bow Tie!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:05.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'll crank up the volume, and—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.04,0:23:07.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.99,0:23:21.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.69,0:23:24.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the door! Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.50,0:23:29.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.83,0:23:31.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.04,0:23:33.84,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Damn it! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:36.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Why is he after Ran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.54,0:23:51.54,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The bandaged man {\i1}is{\i0} after Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.54,0:23:53.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But why her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.64,0:23:56.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's nagging at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.04,0:23:57.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Think back, Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.48,0:24:03.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just figured it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.89,0:24:10.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know who killed Chikako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.49,0:24:15.45,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.45,0:24:20.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Piano wires
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.87,0:24:23.27,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, we can see what's under the bandages!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.87,0:24:24.72,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,An open wound!
